snippet: The Yankees, who have not faced a Washington team that finished as a winner since the 1969 season, will play the Nationals in a matchup of first-place clubs.
abstract: New York Yankees, who have not faced a Washington team that finished as a winner since the 1969 season, are preparing to face the Washington Nationals in a matchup of first-place clubs.
lead_paragraph: The Yankees, who have not faced a Washington team that finished as a winner since the 1969 season, will play the Nationals in a matchup of first-place clubs.
